data.description:
MUST SELL FAST! On the big water of Lake Caroline. 

Exquisite Lakefront Home with Boathouse & Pool!
Experience the epitome of luxury living in this stunning 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom lakefront home nestled in a peaceful corner of Lake Caroline. Boasting a host of exceptional features, including a double lift boathouse, a sparkling in-ground pool, and a 3-car garage, this property offers the ideal retreat for discerning buyers.
Step inside to discover an inviting foyer with a grand 10' solid Mahogany door, unveiling breathtaking views of the formal living room, formal dining room, and elegant staircase. The impressive heart of pine floors and soaring ceilings create a sense of opulence throughout the living spaces.
To the right of the foyer, you'll find the sunlit living room, flooded with natural light and offering private access to the wraparound porch. On the left, the dining room awaits, enhanced by a bay window, wainscoting, and a convenient dry bar with a wine cooler and pass-through to the kitchen.
The gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight, complete with a gas cooktop, built-in oven and microwave, breakfast bar, two serving areas with display cabinetry, a pantry, and a tongue and groove ceiling. The central vacuum, under-cabinet lighting, and ample storage add to the appeal. All appliances are high-end stainless steel.
Adjacent to the kitchen is the great room, featuring a brick accented fireplace and built-ins. Both the breakfast area and great room provide access to the wraparound porch, allowing for seamless indoor-outdoor entertaining.
Down the hall from the foyer, you'll find the luxurious primary suite, boasting its own corner fireplace with a hearth, a private patio, and an ensuite bathroom with separate vanities, a corner jetted tub, a walk-in tiled shower, and an oversized walk-in closet. A glass French door leads to the adjacent office space.
Upstairs, a catwalk landing leads to three additional bedrooms, each offering a walk-in closet, and a bonus/game room. One of the rooms provides semi-private hall access to a spacious guest bathroom. The large bonus room features a dormer, while the Jack and Jill bedrooms offer dormers and double vanities. The laundry room offers ample storage, and the attic is conveniently walk-up accessible.
Outside, the property sits on just under an acre and showcases a sprawling front yard, an enticing pool with generous lounging space, and a 20x20 dock perfect for relaxation or launching kayaks. The wraparound covered patio, private primary suite patio, and double lift boathouse with a 20x10 workshop, sink, and fish table provide an abundance of fantastic entertaining spaces.
With the added benefits and amenities of the Lake Caroline Subdivision, this home is truly a dream come true. Zoned irrigation, landscape lighting, and other thoughtful features further enhance the appeal. Don't miss the opportunity to tour this exceptional property. Call today for your private viewing.
